OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain will clear away this
OL,6,Fmorning. Then a few bright or sunny
OL,7,Fintervals along with scattered
OL,8,Fshowers, some longer spells of rain
OL,9,Facross Argyll. Showers will heavy at
OL,10,Ftimes. Colder than of late.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will see
OL,13,Fscattered showers. Showers gradually
OL,14,Fdying out through the early hours,
OL,15,Fbecoming dry by dawn. A cold night
OL,16,Fwith frost in sheltered glens.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
