OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FDry in the morning with some
OL,6,Fearly sunshine. Dry and cloudier in
OL,7,Fthe afternoon, outbreaks of rain
OL,8,Fspreading northeast in the evening
OL,9,Falong with strengthening southeasterly
OL,10,Fwinds. Rather cold.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMainly
OL,13,Fdry with sunny intervals and just a
OL,14,Ffew showers on Saturday. More in the
OL,15,Fway of showers on Sunday and Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
